data.title: Homeschool Day at Heard Natural Science Museum & Wildlife Sanctuary Aug. 15
data.meta_description: Homeschoolers and their families are invited to join us for a day of fun and learning at the Heard. Reservations are required.
data.text:
Thursday, August 15

McKinney, Texas -- Homeschoolers and their families are invited to join us at Heard Natural Science Museum & Wildlife Sanctuary for a day of fun and learning at the Heard. Families will enjoy a discount on event tickets: buy one, get one of equal of lesser value free.

Join us for special activities and visit with representatives from local organizations!

Reservations are required for the special event.

Plus, participants are welcome to join us for the 3rd Thursday Bird Walk at 8:00 a.m.

Register...

Homeschoolers and their families are invited to join us for a day of fun and learning at the Heard. Families will enjoy a discount on event tickets: buy one, get one of equal of lesser value free. Be sure to use promo code HSDAY2024 when you purchase your tickets. Join us for special activities and visit with representatives from local organizations!

Plus, participants are welcome to join us for the 3rd Thursday Bird Walk at 8 a.m.!

Reservations are required for the special event. Be sure to save your spot today.
